ounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Walter Stowell was born in 1403, his father, Sir Thomas Stowell, was 33 and his mother, Joan Frampton, was 28. He married Joan Farway in 1423, in England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1438, at the age of 35, and was buried in St Thomas Of Canterbury's Church, Cothelstone, Somerset, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1403–1438":"1403–1438","1405–1530":"1405–1530","1408–Female":"1408–Surnud","1405–1423":"1405–1423","1422–1499":"1422–1499","1370–1439":"1370–1439","1375–1436":"1375–1436","1370":"1370","1403":"1403","1436":"1436","1423":"1423","1422":"1422","1499":"1499","1530":"1530","about 1403":"umbes 1403","1375":"1375","26 May 1436":"26. mai 1436","1408":"1408","1439":"1439","1438":"1438","1405":"1405","Somerset, England":"Somerset, England","Church of Saint Thomas of Canterbury, Cothelstone, Somerset West and Taunton district, Somerset, England, United Kingdom":"St Thomas Of Canterbury's Church, Cothelstone, Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cothelstone, Somerset West and Taunton district, Somerset, England, United Kingdom":"Cothelstone, Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cothelstone, Somerset, England":"Cothelstone, Somerset, England","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1403–1438":"1403–1438","1405–1530":"1405–1530","1408–Female":"1408–Kuollut","1405–1423":"1405–1423","1422–1499":"1422–1499","1370–1439":"1370–1439","1375–1436":"1375–1436","1370":"1370","1403":"1403","1436":"1436","1423":"1423","1422":"1422","1499":"1499","1530":"1530","about 1403":"noin 1403","1375":"1375","26 May 1436":"26. toukokuuta 1436","1408":"1408","1439":"1439","1438":"1438","1405":"1405","Somerset, England":"Somerset, England","Church of Saint Thomas of Canterbury, Cothelstone, Somerset West and Taunto